[LAUGH]

00:24:03.480 --> 00:24:04.080 align:middle line:90%


00:24:04.080 --> 00:24:04.880 align:middle line:90%
>> Blow, please.

00:24:04.880 --> 00:24:07.430 align:middle line:90%


00:24:07.430 --> 00:24:10.350 align:middle line:84%
Then after a while, I realized
he wasn't going to stop,

00:24:10.350 --> 00:24:12.410 align:middle line:84%
