any time with him,

00:24:12.410 --> 00:24:13.880 align:middle line:90%
I'd better learn how also.

00:24:13.880 --> 00:24:17.240 align:middle line:90%


00:24:17.240 --> 00:24:20.840 align:middle line:84%
>> We do not sign our
glass with our names.

00:24:20.840 --> 00:24:23.930 align:middle line:84%
We sign our glass
[? the Dance ?] Glass,

