00:24:36.020 --> 00:24:44.870 align:middle line:90%


00:24:44.870 --> 00:24:50.540 align:middle line:10%
>> The piece, that's one of
the things that really said

00:24:50.540 --> 00:24:52.760 align:middle line:10%
it's time for me to
leave Calgary now.

00:24:52.760 --> 00:24:58.600 align:middle line:84%
It's just the pace of the
