00:27:25.560 --> 00:27:30.560 align:middle line:84%
>> You know, as soon as the
weather gets a bit nicer,

00:27:30.560 --> 00:27:33.320 align:middle line:84%
my thoughts turn to starting
the pottery here again.

00:27:33.320 --> 00:27:41.010 align:middle line:90%


00:27:41.010 --> 00:27:47.570 align:middle line:84%
I was a construction engineer,
surveyor in Australia,

00:27:47.570 --> 00:27:48.600 align:middle line:90%
in heavy construction.

00:27:48.600 --> 00:27:51.870 align:middle line:10%
And the last job I'd worked
on there was in Sydney,

00:27:51.870 --> 00:27:54.990 align:middle line:10%
was an expressway right
through the middle of town.

00:27:54.990 --> 00:27:58.680 align:middle line:84%
