see a bit of the world

00:27:58.680 --> 00:28:02.400 align:middle line:84%
before I settled down
[INAUDIBLE],, et cetera,

00:28:02.400 --> 00:28:06.012 align:middle line:84%
and got a job in Toronto on
the [? Spadina ?] Expressway.

00:28:06.012 --> 00:28:07.470 align:middle line:84%
