the back of the school.

00:31:07.035 --> 00:31:08.785 align:middle line:84%
>> What are you guys
trying to do anyways.

00:31:08.785 --> 00:31:10.770 align:middle line:90%
>> [INAUDIBLE]

00:31:10.770 --> 00:31:13.740 align:middle line:84%
>> Immediately, the idea
coalesced into, like,

00:31:13.740 --> 00:31:18.060 align:middle line:84%
an entry portal that had welcome
in English and [INAUDIBLE]----

00:31:18.060 --> 00:31:18.860 align:middle line:90%
what's that?

00:31:18.860 --> 00:31:22.870 align:middle line:90%
[INAUDIBLE] beside it.

00:31:22.870 --> 00:31:27.340 align:middle line:84%
